<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .navbar-brand { font-weight: bold; color: #2d5a27 !important; }
        .bg-primary { background-color: #2d5a27 !important; }
        .btn-primary { background-color: #2d5a27; border-color: #2d5a27; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: #1e3c1a; border-color: #1e3c1a; }
        footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; margin-top: auto; }
        .form-section { border-left: 4px solid #2d5a27; padding-left: 15px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .confirm-value {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            min-height: 38px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .form-label {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">🌸 菊名桜山公園</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">ホーム</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/register">ボランティア登録</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/apply">イベント申込</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/status">登録状況確認</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/admin">管理画面</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container my-4 flex-grow-1">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                    <h2>📋 ボランティア登録状況</h2>
                    <a href="/status" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">別のメールアドレスで検索</a>
                </div>

                <!-- ボランティア登録 -->
                <% if (volunteer) { %>
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-header" style="background-color: #c8e6c9;">
                        <h4 class="mb-0">🌱 ボランティア登録情報</h4>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                            <small class="text-muted">登録日: <%= volunteer.createdAt.toLocaleDateString('ja-JP') %></small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body" style="background-color: #e8f8e8;">
                        <div class="form-section">
                            <h5>📝 基本情報</h5>
                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">登録種別</label>
                                    <div class="confirm-value">
                                        <span class="badge bg-<%= volunteer.type === 'org' ? 'info' : 'primary' %> fs-6">
                                            <%= volunteer.type === 'org' ? '団体' : '個人' %>
                                        </span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label"><%= volunteer.type === 'org' ? '代表者名' : '氏名' %></label>
                                    <div class="confirm-value"><%= volunteer.name %></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <% if (volunteer.orgName) { %>
                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">団体名</label>
                                    <div class="confirm-value"><%= volunteer.orgName %></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>

                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">メールアドレス</label>
                                    <div class="confirm-value"><%= volunteer.email %></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">電話番号</label>
                                    <div class="confirm-value"><%= volunteer.phone || '未入力' %></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <% if (volunteer.address) { %>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">住所</label>
                                <div class="confirm-value"><%= volunteer.address %></div>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>

                        <!-- スキル・経験 -->
                        <div class="form-section">
                            <h5>💡 スキル・経験</h5>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">選択されたスキル</label>
                                <div class="confirm-value">
                                    <%
                                    let skillsData = [];
                                    try {
                                        skillsData = JSON.parse(volunteer.skills || '[]');
                                    } catch (e) {
                                        skillsData = [];
                                    }
                                    %>
                                    <% if (skillsData.length > 0) { %>
                                        <% skillsData.forEach(skill => { %>
                                            <span class="badge bg-secondary me-1"><%= skill %></span>
                                        <% }); %>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <span class="text-muted">選択なし</span>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 興味のある活動 -->
                        <div class="form-section">
                            <h5>🌟 興味のある活動</h5>
                            <%
                            let interestsData = [];
                            let conservationData = [];
                            try {
                                const interestsParts = (volunteer.interests || '').split('|');
                                if (interestsParts[0]) {
                                    interestsData = JSON.parse(interestsParts[0]);
                                }
                                if (interestsParts[1]) {
                                    conservationData = JSON.parse(interestsParts[1]);
                                }
                            } catch (e) {
                                // ignore
                            }
                            %>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">一般活動</label>
                                <div class="confirm-value">
                                    <% if (interestsData.length > 0) { %>
                                        <% interestsData.forEach(interest => { %>
                                            <span class="badge bg-info me-1"><%= interest %></span>
                                        <% }); %>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <span class="text-muted">選択なし</span>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">保全活動</label>
                                <div class="confirm-value">
                                    <% if (conservationData.length > 0) { %>
                                        <% conservationData.forEach(activity => { %>
                                            <span class="badge bg-success me-1"><%= activity %></span>
                                        <% }); %>
                                    <% } else { %>
                                        <span class="text-muted">選択なし</span>
                                    <% } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <% if (volunteer.notes) { %>
                        <div class="form-section">
                            <h5>💬 備考・メッセージ</h5>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">その他ご質問・ご要望等</label>
                                <div class="confirm-value" style="white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 60px;">
                                    <%= volunteer.notes %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
                        
                        <!-- 連絡先案内 -->
                        <div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
                            <h6>📞 変更ご希望の場合</h6>
                            <p class="mb-0">登録内容の変更をご希望の場合は、菊名桜山公園愛護会までご連絡ください。<br>
                            <strong>連絡先:</strong> osawa-s@nifty.com</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <% if (!volunteer) { %>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <div class="display-4">📭</div>
                            <h5>ボランティア登録情報が見つかりません</h5>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-muted">入力されたメールアドレスでのボランティア登録は見つかりませんでした。</p>
                        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-center">
                            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary me-md-2">ボランティア登録する</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="text-center mt-4">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">ホームに戻る</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="py-3 mt-4">
        <div class="container text-center text-muted">
            <p>&copy; 2025 菊名桜山公園 ボランティア管理システム</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>